<p>Very cool idea. Adding GOIs like Fuller and AWCY to the setting really works and it's welcome to have portrayals of Sarkicism that are outside of the binary proto vs neo classification. As very minor criticism it feels like the Cotton Eye Joe character could use a rename, it comes across a bit Colonel Sandersery.</p>

